note.p:
Depicts the Last Judgment. Christ is enthroned on the arc of heaven;
							below kneel the Virgin and St. John the Baptist. Above are 2 angel
							musicians playing the trumpet.

Various illustrations depict the birth of the Virgin, St. Anne and the
							Virgin, within initial letter "D"; a monkey, within initial letter "V";
							a grotesque, within initial letter "A".

Various illustrations depict the Lamentation, within initial letter "D";
							a swan, within initial letter "B"; animals, within initial letter
							"S".

Depicts 5 lines of 5-stave notation of the Bassus part. In margin: Ludwig
							Senfl playing a positive organ; a mass scene; the birth of Christ;
							singing clerics.
